Enhance Message Engagement Tracking with More MobilePush Events

Receive near real-time updates on message delivery and engagement by subscribing to eight new MobilePush events introduced in Event Notification Service (ENS). Serve reporting and retargeting uses cases by moving data off the Marketing Cloud Engagement platform at scale.

Where: This change applies to all Marketing Cloud Engagement editions.

Who: Users with Event Notification Service permissions can configure subscriptions to consume ENS events.

How: You can now add these MobilePush events.

Push Sent
Push Not Sent
Push Bounced
Push Open
In-App Delivered
In-App Displayed
In-App Dismissed
Inbox Open
title: Enhance Mobile Message Tracking with New Events
